    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款单人循环圈塔防！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需实时建设不同空间防卫设施，构建属于自己的防卫阵地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/cf30de482fef3cba441933d4d8c8ea20.poster.avif?t=1766248538\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/cf30de482fef3cba441933d4d8c8ea20.webm?t=1766248538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/cf30de482fef3cba441933d4d8c8ea20.mp4?t=1766248538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击退敌人，保证我方的能量循环！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/48c228f9241b3b9ea70430e0ba041cee.poster.avif?t=1766248538\" width=618 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/48c228f9241b3b9ea70430e0ba041cee.webm?t=1766248538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/48c228f9241b3b9ea70430e0ba041cee.mp4?t=1766248538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在空间循环站中，您每一轮的选择都至关重要。选择和升级您的防卫设施！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/cee3605cb6e811b463f0453b3842727d.poster.avif?t=1766248538\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162110/extras/cee3605cb6e811b463f0453b3842727d.webm?t=1766248538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><sour